import { Icon } from "@iconify/react";
import { Button, Container, Stack, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Card,
  Chip,
  Divider,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemDecorator,
} from "@mui/joy";

export default function ExperienceTimelinePart() {
  return (
    <Container
      maxWidth="fluid"
      sx={{ backgroundColor: "#0D0D0D", pt: 15, pb: 15 }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Stack
          direction="row"
          alignItems="center"
          justifyContent="center"
          mb={5}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h4"
            gutterBottom
            color="white"
            textAlign="center"
            sx={{
              background:
                "linear-gradient(primary,primary) left 0 bottom 10% /100% 20% no-repeat",
            }}
          >
            Experience
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
        <Card
          size="lg"
          variant="outlined"
          sx={{ backgroundColor: "transparent", border: "thin solid white" }}
        >
          <Chip size="sm" variant="outlined" color="neutral">
            BASIC
          </Chip>
          <Typography level="h2">Professional</Typography>
          <Divider inset="none" />
          <List size="sm" sx={{ mx: "calc(-1 * var(--ListItem-paddingX))" }}>
            <ListItem>
              <ListItemDecorator>
                <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
              </ListItemDecorator>
              Virtual Credit Cards
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <ListItemDecorator>
                <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
              </ListItemDecorator>
              Financial Analytics
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <ListItemDecorator>
                <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
              </ListItemDecorator>
              Checking Account
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem>
              <ListItemDecorator>
                <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
              </ListItemDecorator>
              API Integration
            </ListItem>
          </List>
        </Card>
        <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" width="100%" mt={10}>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            size="large"
            component={Link}
            to={"../experience"}
            sx={{
              backgroundColor: "primary",
              color: "black",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              borderRadius: 2,
              width: 150,
            }}
          >
            See More
          </Button>
        </Stack>
      </Container>
    </Container>
  );
}
